enums.name: RunStatus

values.name: queued
values.doc: Represents a run that is queued to start.

values.name: inProgress
values.doc: Represents a run that is in progress.

values.name: requiresAction
values.doc: Represents a run that needs another operation, such as tool output submission, to continue.

values.name: cancelling
values.doc: Represents a run that is in the process of cancellation.

values.name: cancelled
values.doc: Represents a run that has been cancelled.

values.name: failed
values.doc: Represents a run that failed.

values.name: completed
values.doc: Represents a run that successfully completed.

values.name: expired
values.doc: Represents a run that expired before it could otherwise finish.

enums.doc: Possible values for the status of an assistant thread run.

enums.name: RunStepType

values.name: messageCreation
values.doc: Represents a run step to create a message.

values.name: toolCalls
values.doc: Represents a run step that calls tools.

enums.name: RunStepStatus

values.name: inProgress
values.doc: Represents a run step still in progress.

values.name: cancelled
values.doc: Represents a run step that was cancelled.

values.name: failed
values.doc: Represents a run step that failed.

values.name: completed
values.doc: Represents a run step that successfully completed.

values.name: expired
values.doc: Represents a run step that expired before otherwise finishing.

enums.name: RunStepErrorCode

values.name: serverError

values.name: rateLimitExceeded
